description: Rarely available at The Foundry! Renovated 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom home with a bonus lofted area ideal for a guest room or additional storage! This residence features engineered hardwood floors and sky high soaring ceilings. The absolute epitome of classic brick and beam construction make this a special home full of character and amazing scale of space! The kitchen is complete with updated stainless steel appliances, Premium Granite stone countertops. Oversized 8' Windows with custom window treatments. Lives much larger than the actual square footage! This stylish, contemporary city home is an exceptional opportunity in today's market! Professionally managed, elevator building with laundry and bike storage. Minutes to Broadway, the best South Boston hot spots & restaurants, the Seaport District, Broadway T Station or Downtown!!! Beautiful building in an absolutely AAA neighborhood! Make your number one resolution come true with this wonderful home!
